data.description: Nestled in the Heart of Jackson, just follow the yellow brick road on down to this 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Sprawling Ranch completely updated and turnkey on just over an acre of property.  There 's absolutely ''NO PLACE LIKE HOME'' when viewing the numerous upgrades and updates which include Pella Windows, Pergo Flooring, completely updated kitchen with Granite C-tops, Professional Frigidaire Series Appliance pkg, Newer tankless hot water heater, Upgraded Electric Service, Newer AC Unit, Newer Siding, New front patio & walkway, New Stone Rear Patio, Newer sliders which leads to your spacious outdoor area built to entertain or just relax in your fenced in private backyard space. Owner did all the work, you just move in !!! Excellent schools and so much more!
